had to get off my IG hiatus for this one. been in the trenches with @ericbellinger last 7 months. from the first time he played me this project to going through 50 different versions. ive listened front to back countless times & have yet to get tired of it. congrats e, you really put r&b on your back. & the alien work ethic is insane lol i haven’t met an artist that does EVERYTHING & we both know i mean everything. thanks for trusting the vision while still being in the field providing guidance each step. we sure did put our foot in this roll out..by any means necessary!! *khaledvoice i tried my best to document some of our processes (i’ll be better). nothing but love to all my creative collaborators who make my job look easy & to everyone who help this machine move. 1(800) hit-eazy line 2 out now 📞📞🦾🦾
korea is the silver lining 🇰🇷✨ 감사합니다 to everybody who helped make this trip so special..y’all know who you are 🤝🙏🫡

back in feb i got a call from @djscoobdoo. said i had 10 hours to put together a quick shoot for wayne. i did what i always do. don’t think too much & just act. weezy a real goat to me. we grew up to his music. WE’VE PAID A PROMOTER to open up for him in a past life lol fast forward to this past tuesday i’m in my home state creative producing & giving edit notes for content to kick off his tour. FULL CIRCLE. the biggest thank you to scoob for the opportunity to deliver. @offthecheng for the edits & unselfishly being there with me every step of the way. 🙏 @jasminenkelly for connecting the dots. PHOTOS BY ME. #dontaskmewhatidoaskmewhatidontdo

new single #super co-written by @augamatic from the new @saythename_17 album ‘fml’ out now! congratulations to my bro @bumzu91. i know how hard ya’ll been working & the results are 🔥🦾 record came out insane #songsbysummerchild 🌻

co-directing this spot was not on my 23’ bingo card but WHAT AN HONOR. concept by the legend himself @llcoolj, couldn’t of done this without his vision. @bennybankskid @jasminenkelly the mission ain’t a mission without you two. thank you to ll’s team & @livenationurban for letting us rock 🙏🦾 #dontaskmewhatidoaskmewhatidontdo
